  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. All 13 credibility factors assessed at high rigor; achievedLevel meets or exceeds requiredLevel for each factor. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification and global sensitivity analysis are linked as structured evidence. Decision: Accepted.",
