      "rationale": "The CFD solver (OpenFOAM v9) is maintained under ISO 9001-compliant quality management. Full regression test suite (847 cases) passes on each release. Version control, issue tracking, and change-control procedures documented and audited. Achieved level 5: independent third-party SQA audit completed with no major findings."
