      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/synth/criteria/code-verification-mrl5-requirements",
      "rationale": "Method of manufactured solutions (MMS) applied to incompressible Navier-Stokes and scalar transport equations. Observed convergence order matches theoretical order (2nd-order in space, 1st-order in time) for all relevant PDEs. MMS tests archived in the project verification repository and independently reproduced by a second analyst."
