      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/synth/criteria/input-equivalency-mrl5-requirements",
      "rationale": "Computational boundary conditions (inlet velocity profile, rotational speed, fluid properties) verified against experimentally measured values for each operating condition. Discrepancies between nominal and measured conditions documented and propagated as input uncertainty. Geometric fidelity confirmed by comparing CAD model to pump metrology report (dimensional tolerances < 0.05 mm on critical passages)."
    }
